Package severinnitsche.com.github

Class SortAndSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • severinnitsche.com.github.SortAndSearch

  • public class SortAndSearch
extends java.lang.Object
    The SortAndSearch class provides methods to sort and search different data structures.

    The Non Array structures are provided within it

    Data Structures:

    • LinkedList
    • BinaryTree

    Sorting Algortihms:

    • Bubbles Sort
    • Binary Tree Sort
    • Quick Sort
    • Radix Sort MSD / LSD

    Searching Algorithms:

    • Linear Search
    • Binary Tree Search
